CatDescriptText: Reverend Williams, of Baptist Temple Church in Homewood, sits on a stoop and shows a group of boys a model of a World War II two-engine fighter airplane.
TitMainTitle: Reverend Williams of Baptist Temple Church in Homewood holding model Lockheed P-38 Lightning fighter airplane surrounded by boys, including Carl R. Southers, on right in background and Kenneth Hawthorne to his right, gathered on steps outside stone building
